WEBVTT

00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:31.536
I decided I wanted to join the WWE.

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:32.776
So that's also me.

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:35.216
(Laughter)

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:38.936
Sure you remember me
from Monday Night Raw in 2002 and 2003,

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.416
and I had a blast

00:00:40.440 --> 00:00:42.976
playing what people
affectionately like to call

00:00:43.000 --> 00:00:45.176
Chris Harvard, the Ivy League snob.

00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:46.976
(Laughter)

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:48.296
It was perfect for me.

00:00:48.320 --> 00:00:50.416
But unfortunately,

00:00:50.440 --> 00:00:54.296
I got kicked in the head
by my colleague Bubba Ray Dudley,

00:00:54.320 --> 00:00:56.296
and I suffered a severe concussion.

